These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, comedy
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | comedy |
| Transport     | motorbike | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, broccoli
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | lime      | broccoli         |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: papaya, lime
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice   |
| Food       | lime  | papaya |

 #################################

 
